long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
All Images Downloader enables users to download all images from the current webpage, including lazy-loaded and original images with one click. All of the images are saved in a ZIP file on your machine.

This extension helps people to avoid manually downloading each and every image they want. Since the images downloaded are of the highest possible quality, users save time and energy.
